---
import WaxSeal from "@components/WaxSeal.astro";
---

<aside
  class="mt-16 border-t border-default pt-10"
  aria-label="About the author"
>
  <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
    <div class="shrink-0">
      <WaxSeal orientation="mark-only" size={56} />
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow text-[11.5px]">Heritage Strategies</p>
      <p class="mt-2 font-display font-medium text-[1.4rem] leading-snug text-ink">
        The Heritage Strategies team.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-ink-muted font-editorial">
        Heritage is an estate-planning multi-family office founded in 2009. The partners hold over sixty years of combined experience with ultra-high-net-worth families, generational handoffs, and the operating companies that built the wealth. Writing here is collective; specific authorship is named when an individual partner is the right voice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>
